{
  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "Zhang et al. [354] introduced the Persona-Chat dataset with 5 million personas to train models for more personalized dialogues.",
    "Mazaré et al. [190] created a dataset of over 700 million conversations extracted from Reddit, demonstrating the effectiveness of training dialogue models on large-scale personal profiles.",
    "P 2 Bot [172] generates personalized and consistent dialogues by simulating the perception of personalities between conversation participants.",
    "DHAP [184] designs a novel Transformer structure to automatically learn implicit user profiles from dialogue history without explicit personal information.",
    "Wu et al. [322] propose a generative segmentation memory network to integrate diverse personal information."
  ],
